    "patch_code": "private boolean inferTemplated typesforcall(\n    node n, functionType fnType){\n  final immutablelist< templateType> Keys = fntype.get templateTypeMap().get template Keys();\n  if ( Keys.isEmpty()) {return false};\n  \n  // try to infer the template types\n  map< templateType,jsType> infered = infer template typesfrom parameters(ftype, n);\n \n  //Replace all template types. If we couldn't find a replacation, we replacit withUNKown\n  templateType replacer = new templateType replacer(registry, infered);\n  node call target = n. get firstchild();\n  functionType replacementFnType = fntype. visit(replacer). tomaybefunctionType();\n  preconditions. check null(replacingFnType);\n  call target. setjsType(replacingFnType);\n  n. setjsType(replacingFnType. get ReturnType());\n  return replacer. made changes;\n};",
