    "patch_code": "private boolean inferTemplated types for call(\n    node n, function type) {\n  final imm ut = type.get ut();\n  \n  if (!ut.isEmpty()) {\n    return false;\n  }\n  \n  // try to infer the Template types\n  map infered = infer Template types From parameters(type, n);\n  \n  //Replace all Template types. If we couldn't find a replacer, we\n  Template type replacer = new Template type replacer(registry, infered);\n  node call target = n.get first child();\n  \n  function type replacement = type. visit(replacer)\n    . to maybe function type();\n  preconditions. check null(replacing function type);\n  \n  call target. setjs type(replacing function type);\n  n. setjs type(replacing function type. get rpt);\n  \n  return replacer. made changes;\n}",
